Package: fitnessTracker
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Analyzing and Visualizing Health and Fitness
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Hannah", "Hillery",
      email = "hannah.hillery1@yahoo.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package contains tools for analysing and visualizing health and fitness data from fitbit or apple watches. 
  The package comes with a sets of data that range in categories from sleep, activity, and weight health. Functions in this package
  include viusalization tools to show trends in activity types and levels, along with sleep and weight changes. This package also includes
  functions to analyze health calculations, trends, and summarize the data.
